Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.21,0:00:20.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How's Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.98,0:00:22.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.38,0:00:24.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she wants to take a shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.36,0:00:26.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you want me to check on her one more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.38,0:00:29.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You can't! Not now...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.26,0:00:30.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.65,0:00:33.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.22,0:00:36.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The second match is starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.30,0:00:45.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This kinda thing gets the \Nblood pumpin', ya know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.49,0:02:26.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first day of the Grand Magic Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.49,0:02:31.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle part continues \Nwith the second match,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.64,0:02:34.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,featuring Ren Akatsuki of Blue Pegasus versus
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.95,0:02:37.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Arania Webb of Mermaid Heel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.98,0:02:42.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad Omen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:48.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you've improved \Nsince last year, Arania.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.42,0:02:54.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure it's okay for a member of \NBlue Pegasus to attack a woman, Ren-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.60,0:02:57.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like both opponents \Nare standing their ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:02:59.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be a good match!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:02.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ren-kun, good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:05.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sherry is cheering you on from the stands!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.55,0:03:16.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wide open, Ren-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.41,0:03:19.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ren, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.46,0:03:21.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:24.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out, Sherry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.04,0:03:26.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't root for members of an enemy team!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:29.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on, Obaba. They {\i1}are{\i0} engaged...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:31.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:32.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Spin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:36.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm spinning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:39.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who says we're engaged?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.67,0:03:41.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We just happen to be stuck \Nwith each other is all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.79,0:03:43.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.13,0:03:48.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's annoying the way you're \Nalways by my side...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:51.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:55.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...when you're not with \Nme, I can't get into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:03:59.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.19,0:04:01.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ren...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:04.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sherry sure fell in love \Nwith a pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.94,0:04:07.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's love...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.48,0:04:10.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The one thing I can't do is look lame
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.90,0:04:12.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,in front of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:23.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aerial Phose!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:39.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He won!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:43.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The winner... Ren Akatsuki of Blue Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.94,0:04:47.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, Blue Pegasus has \N14 points for the first day!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.37,0:04:49.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mermaid Heel has three points!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.17,0:04:53.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot... I let down my guard...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:56.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Ren-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.58,0:05:01.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Unsurprisingly, he's improved \Ncompared to seven years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:03.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that Ichiya's \Ngotten stronger, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:06.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.96,0:05:09.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichiya has always been a man to reckon with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.54,0:05:11.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His personality leaves \Nsomething to be desired,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.13,0:05:14.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but there's no denying that he's \NBlue Pegasus's strongest wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:17.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.43,0:05:18.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichiya, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.67,0:05:22.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I suddenly wanna fight him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:25.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But what bothers me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.34,0:05:27.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,is that person in the bunny costume.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:30.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So it is alright to be bugged by that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:34.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! I thought maybe we \Nweren't supposed to mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.29,0:05:42.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next up, the third match of day one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.97,0:05:45.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,War Cry of Quatro Cerberus
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:50.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,versus Orga Nanagear of Team Sabertooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.60,0:05:51.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.92,0:05:53.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Orga!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:54.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kick his ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.48,0:05:57.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to those cheers! The crowd loves him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:06:00.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can beat him, War Cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.21,0:06:03.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your soul is always wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:07.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's War Cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:11.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta see this. I like that guy's magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:13.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly, it is amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.28,0:06:14.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:16.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.73,0:06:34.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only interested... in you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:35.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Gajeel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:39.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally get to see a Sabertooth battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:43.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he's as strong \Nas that masked ball guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.15,0:06:47.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think is gonna win, Lecter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.08,0:06:49.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Orga-kun, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:52.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:56.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sting-kun is number one, but \Neveryone in Sabertooth is strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:07:01.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are dumb, Frosch, \Nif you don't even know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.21,0:07:03.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fro thinks so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:07.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let the third match begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:28.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is! War Cry's Tear Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:31.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a funny phrase, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.03,0:07:33.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:34.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tear Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:36.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of magic is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:49.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The more I cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:55.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...the stronger I get!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.41,0:08:13.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.19,0:08:18.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Lightning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:20.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One... attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.65,0:08:23.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The match is over! Literally, in a flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.78,0:08:27.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Orga's Black Lightning fried \Nthe tears instantaneously!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.60,0:08:30.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.06,0:08:31.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Instantaneously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:33.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:36.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's strong! I mean, really strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.52,0:08:40.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The winner is Orga Nanagear of Sabertooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.44,0:08:42.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That brings their total to 20 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.81,0:08:45.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A perfect first day!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:48.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Quatro Cerberus has two points! Too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:54.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you have made it more fun, Orga?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.98,0:08:58.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sing a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.23,0:09:01.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.20,0:09:03.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mic!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:10.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my! What does Orga Nanagear want to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:15.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest, the strongest, number one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:19.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the leaders, Sabertooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:23.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest, the strongest, number one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:27.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the leaders, Sabertooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:31.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The strongest, the strongest, number one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:31.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They really do have raw \Npower... and popularity...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:35.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}We're the leaders, Sabertooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:33.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the strongest guild, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.31,0:09:37.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to admit it, but \Nthose guys are impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.53,0:09:42.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, it's time for the \Nfinal match of the first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:47.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The teams that are left are Fairy \NTail B and Lamia Scale, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.29,0:09:51.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, these two guilds were \Nabout equal in terms of talent,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:54.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so this should be an interesting match!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.46,0:09:59.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll announce the first day's \Nfinal fight match-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:04.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Mystogan of Fairy Tail B versus
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.44,0:10:08.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jura Neekis of Lamia Scale!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:11.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:12.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jura!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.55,0:10:15.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting to see Jura!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.25,0:10:18.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought he'd participate \Nfrom the first day!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:21.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:23.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And his opponent is Jura!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:27.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even in Fairy Tail, those who \Nknow his true face are few...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.65,0:10:29.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The mysterious wizard, Mystogan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.88,0:10:31.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the heck is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.47,0:10:32.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.73,0:10:39.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Jura-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.19,0:10:41.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This match is as good as over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.01,0:10:42.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't even started yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.97,0:10:45.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that. Stifle yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.88,0:10:49.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Jura!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:51.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jura's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:53.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the real thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:57.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That Jura person sure is popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.18,0:11:01.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sure. He's one of the \NTen Great Wizard Saints.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.29,0:11:04.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The same as our master...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.44,0:11:06.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is unlucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.76,0:11:09.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Going up against Jura...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:12.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that cueball really that strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.95,0:11:16.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know if Erza and I \Ncould beat him working together...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.14,0:11:20.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.30,0:11:55.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Personally, I'm rooting for Fairy Tail,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:58.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but our Obaba is really strict about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.67,0:12:07.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies, but I'm not \Ngoing to hold back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.21,0:12:09.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.12,0:12:14.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't exactly what I'm here for,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:18.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but being able to fight \Non behalf of Fairy Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.87,0:12:20.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing could make me happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.53,0:12:33.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to worry, First \NMaster. It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.91,0:12:36.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That man was once a Wizard Saint himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.99,0:12:39.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you could \Nsay their talents are equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.81,0:12:43.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.29,0:12:46.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I want to go to the ladies' room...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:49.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you're a ghost?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:53.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal... Will you be okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:06.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?! Jellal's going to fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.91,0:13:08.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His cover won't be blown, will it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.74,0:13:11.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I pray he doesn't make a mess of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.63,0:13:17.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mainly, I hope he doesn't \Ntry to impress Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:21.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jura Neekis of Lamia Scale versus
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:24.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mystogan of Fairy Tail B!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.73,0:13:27.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let the final match of the day...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.52,0:13:29.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.28,0:13:32.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What I can do for Fairy Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:36.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...is beat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:52.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.73,0:14:11.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Five Layered Magic Circle... Sacred Song!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:23.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's copying Mystogan's magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.16,0:14:24.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Clever...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:25.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jura-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.91,0:14:27.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.09,0:14:30.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With apologies to Juvia's team,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:35.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe Jura-san is \NFiore's number one wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:38.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Three Layered Magic Circle... Mirror Water!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.73,0:14:43.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It ricocheted!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.38,0:14:44.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:50.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It turned again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.26,0:15:01.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's some kind of strong! He isn't called \None of the Ten Great Wizard Saints for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.97,0:15:04.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Jura! Hurry up and finish him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.94,0:15:06.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Send him spinning!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.23,0:15:07.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're spinning me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.29,0:15:18.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As I suspected, he's not an opponent \NI can beat with borrowed magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.29,0:15:22.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Meteor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.07,0:15:25.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:29.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:33.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Rock Wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:51.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:55.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.31,0:16:03.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Circles in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.32,0:16:04.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When did he...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:07.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He must have drawn them while \Ndefending from the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.36,0:16:12.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be judged by the seven stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.96,0:16:14.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Chariot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:24.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock Mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.91,0:16:43.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.54,0:16:46.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:51.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So Makarov-dono wasn't being \Nentirely candid with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.48,0:16:53.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Makarov-dono...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:56.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A gathering of the Ten Great \NWizard Saints is coming soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.13,0:17:01.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...but before then, I'd like you \Nto tell me about a certain guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.89,0:17:04.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was on guard then,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.31,0:17:08.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but I never imagined you would \Npose as a member of Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.76,0:17:12.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My vigilance was for naught.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.66,0:17:18.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to win for Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.45,0:17:22.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Ultear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:24.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to use that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.18,0:17:28.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?! Jellal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.63,0:17:31.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No! If you use that, your \Ncover will be blown!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.95,0:17:35.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,True Heavenly Body Magic... Cerma!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:47.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:54.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is he thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:58.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what's wrong with men! Their \Npride gets the better of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.42,0:18:00.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Ul?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.47,0:18:17.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The inside of my mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.07,0:18:25.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Spicy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:32.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat more red pepper!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.69,0:18:33.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.91,0:18:35.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's spicy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:43.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What on Earthland is happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.42,0:18:46.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly, Mystogan is in agony!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.01,0:18:48.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.53,0:18:51.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Ul!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.04,0:19:01.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, he's started laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.64,0:19:08.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got more...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.41,0:19:11.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.74,0:19:13.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:18.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take any more! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.81,0:19:37.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.77,0:19:43.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really understand \Nit, but Mystogan is down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.46,0:19:45.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:49.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't afford to let \NJellal stand out too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.07,0:19:56.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The winner is Jura Neekis of Lamia Scale!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.64,0:20:00.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You did great, Jura!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:02.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:06.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And with this, the first day of the \NGrand Magic Games comes to a close!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.41,0:20:09.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the overall ranking!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.55,0:20:14.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A team has zero points and \NB team has one point?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.97,0:20:16.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's awful...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.74,0:20:20.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We shouldn't have participated \Nin this thing after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.23,0:20:28.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Yajima-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:30.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no surprise that \NSabertooth is number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.55,0:20:33.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, Fairy \NTail, which has two teams,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.40,0:20:36.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,is in 7th and 8th place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:38.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still just the first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.85,0:20:42.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hoping for a comeback \Ndrama from tomorrow on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.91,0:20:45.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And my guild still has a shot at victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:47.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait for day two!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.00,0:20:51.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yajima-san, Jenny-san, thank you \Nvery much for your commentary today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.95,0:20:53.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank {\i1}you{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.33,0:20:55.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See you all again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.71,0:21:00.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.83,0:21:03.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he, in charge of Fairy Tail's gags?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.19,0:21:04.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:06.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.89,0:21:09.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.09,0:21:11.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Meldy's doing, most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.79,0:21:15.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell were you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.49,0:21:16.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good try.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:18.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lame...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.39,0:21:21.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even find the words to respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.93,0:21:26.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.44,0:21:28.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.62,0:21:30.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.54,0:21:38.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Last place...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.42,0:21:41.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the end of the first \Nday of the Grand Magic Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.20,0:21:46.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We, Fairy Tail, made a terrible showing...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.98,0:21:51.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...but little did we know that even more \Nterrible events were already in motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.62,0:21:55.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's ripening...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.61,0:22:01.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Several days after the end \Nof the Grand Magic Games...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.86,0:22:03.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...I wrote this down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.84,0:22:06.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is for you, my dear \Nfriend, Lucy Heartfilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.67,0:22:08.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From Levy McGarden.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.81,0:22:13.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What was that?! A prophecy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.85,0:22:18.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Lucy! I'll be in it tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.77,0:22:21.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I swear I'll turn things around for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.67,0:23:58.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, we're in last place! \NWe have zero points!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.46,0:24:00.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! We'll turn the tables \Non 'em starting now!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.61,0:24:02.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially with me participatin' \Nin the next competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.81,0:24:05.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Chariot", huh? I wonder what \Nkind of competition that'll be...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.24,0:24:07.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what kind of \Ncompetition, I'm gonna win it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.52,0:24:10.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like that jerk from Saber \Nand Gajeel are gonna be in it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.47,0:24:12.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter! I'm gonna win!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.20,0:24:13.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.11,0:24:16.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Chariot!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.76,0:24:19.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But "Chariot", that's like a \Nvehicle pulled by horses, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.97,0:24:21.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A vehicle...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.14,0:24:22.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a bad feeling about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.27,0:24:24.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! See ya from the winner's circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.28,0:24:26.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
